  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will address the treatment rate and control rate of hypertension, treatment
      pattern and factors that affect BP control by examining retrospective medical records of
      hypertension patients recovering from stroke, among outpatients coming to the Neurology
      Department in 10 university hospitals nationwide.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
